<item>
            <title>[DATAMONGO-238] @Query and Pageable doesn&apos;t work</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-238</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After having run a bunch of tests I can see that if I have an interface method annotated with @Query and I pass a Pageable into that method, the Pageable will not get picked up and I will instead get returned the entire result set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Mac OS X 10.7</environment>
